Nvidia’s big plans
</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.longandshort.com/email/images/Blackwell-Ultra-Vera-Rubin-AI-platform-chip-system.png" alt="Blackwell Ultra is part of the Vera Rubin AI platform chip system" href="https://www.longandshort.com" />
